    "This allows for more personalized and accurate premium calculations that improve pricing accuracy and risk assessment.",
    "Similarly, the paper by Gao et al. (2022) enhances classical actuarial regression models for claim frequency prediction by incorporating telematics car driving data.",
    "The authors utilize data-driven neural network approaches, including a densely connected feed-forward neural network and a convolutional neural network, to process the telematics data.",
    "The authors integrate it with traditional risk factors, demonstrating the synergistic effect for achieving the best predictive models in automotive insurance.",
    "The paper by Reimers and Shiller (2018) provides an empirical analysis of the impact of \"Pay How You Drive\" (PHYD) insurance programs on fatal accidents and profits in the automotive insurance industry."
